1.1 1.任选一个定性变量，绘制条形图。

# 7.1 ggplot2 绘图: mpg
# 数据：mpg {ggplot2}
# 在完成上述图形时，尽可能美化图形、完善坐标轴、图形标题、主题、颜色等的设置。



mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(fct_infreq(class)))+
  geom_bar(fill = 5)+
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = after_stat(count)),
            vjust = -0.5, size = 3)+
  labs(title = "Barplot of Class",
       subtitle = "38 Popular Models of Cars from 1999 to 2008",
       x = "Class")+
  guides(x = guide_axis(angle = 45))+
  theme_bw()

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(fct_infreq(drv)))+
  geom_bar(fill = 6)+
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = after_stat(count)),
            vjust = -0.5, size = 3)+
  labs(title = "Barplot of the Type of Drive Train",
       subtitle = "38 Popular Models of Cars from 1999 to 2008",
       x = "Type of Drive Train")+
  scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Front-wheel", "Four-wheel", "Rear-wheel"))+
  theme_bw()

# fuel type:
#   r: Regular Gasoline 85~87
#   p: Premium Gasoline  91~95
#   e: E85 85% ethanol乙醇 and 15% gasoline汽油 
#   d: Diesel 
#   c: ?

mpg %>% 
    ggplot(aes(fct_infreq(fl)))+
  geom_bar(fill = 6)+
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = after_stat(count)),
            vjust = -0.5, size = 3)+
  labs(title = "Barplot of the Fuel Type",
       subtitle = "38 Popular Models of Cars from 1999 to 2008",
       x = "Type of Drive Train")+
  scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Regular", "Premium", "E85",
                              "Diesel", "c"))+
  theme_bw()

1.2 2. 任选两个定性变量，绘制分组条形图

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(class, fill = drv))+
  geom_bar(position = "dodge")+
  labs(title = "Grouped Barplot by Class and Drive",
       subtitle = "38 Popular Models of Cars from 1999 to 2008",
       x = "Type of Drive Train")+
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = ..count..),
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.9), vjust = -0.5)+
  scale_fill_discrete(label = c("Four-wheel",
                                "Front-wheel",
                                "Rear-Wheel"))+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(manufacturer, fill = drv))+
  geom_bar(position = "dodge")+
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = ..count..),
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.9), hjust = -0.5)+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,30))+
  coord_flip()+
  labs(title = "Grouped Barplot by Class and Drive",
       subtitle = "38 Popular Models of Cars from 1999 to 2008",
       x = "Type of Drive Train")+
  scale_fill_discrete(label = c("Four-wheel",
                                "Front-wheel",
                                "Rear-Wheel"))+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(class, fill = drv))+
  geom_bar(position = "stack")+
  labs(title = "Grouped Barplot by Class and Drive",
       subtitle = "38 Popular Models of Cars from 1999 to 2008",
       x = "Type of Drive Train")+
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = ..count..),
            position = position_stack(vjust = 0.5))+
  scale_fill_discrete(label = c("Four-wheel",
                                "Front-wheel",
                                "Rear-Wheel"))+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(class, fill = drv))+
  geom_bar(position = "fill")+
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = ..count..),
            position = position_fill(vjust = 0.5))+
  scale_fill_discrete(label = c("Four-wheel",
                                "Front-wheel",
                                "Rear-Wheel"))+
  labs(title = "Grouped Barplot by Class and Drive",
       x = "Type of Drive Train")+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")

1.3 3. 任选一个定量变量，绘制直方图。

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cty))+
  geom_histogram(col = 1,fill = 5, binwidth = 2)+
  stat_bin(aes(label = ifelse(after_stat(count) == 0,
                              "", after_stat(count))), 
           binwidth = 2, 
           geom = "text",vjust = -0.5)+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,60), breaks = seq(0,60,10))+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(9,35,2))+
  labs(title = "Histogram of City Miles per Gallon",
       x = "City Miles per Gallon")

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(hwy))+
  geom_histogram(col = 1,fill = 6, binwidth = 2)+
  stat_bin(aes(label = ifelse(after_stat(count) == 0,
                              "", after_stat(count))), 
           binwidth = 2, 
           geom = "text",vjust = -0.5)+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,60), breaks = seq(0,60,10))+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(11,45,4))+
  labs(title = "Histogram of Highway Miles per Gallon",
       x = "Highway Miles per Gallon")

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cty))+
  geom_histogram(col = 1,fill = 5, binwidth = 2)+
  
  stat_bin(aes(label = ifelse(after_stat(count) == 0,
                              "", after_stat(count))), 
           binwidth = 2, 
           geom = "text",vjust = -0.5)+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,60), breaks = seq(0,60,10))+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(9,35,2))+
  labs(title = "Histogram of City Miles per Gallon",
       x = "City MPG")

# 绘制直方图

ggplot(mpg, aes(x = cty)) + 
  geom_histogram(aes(fill = "City"), binwidth = 2, 
                 color = "black", alpha = 0.5) + 
  geom_histogram(aes(x = hwy, fill = "Highway"), 
                 binwidth = 2, color = "black", alpha = 0.5) + 
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,40), breaks = seq(0,60,10))+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(9,45,2))+
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("cyan", "darkorchid"), 
                    labels = c("City", "Highway"))+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")+
  labs(title = "Histogram of Miles per Gallon",
       x = "Miles per Gallon",
       fill = "")

1.4 4.任选一个定量变量，两个定性变量，绘制分组直方图

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cty,fill = drv))+
  geom_histogram()+
  facet_wrap(~ class, ncol = 1)+
  labs(title = "Histogram of City Miles per Gallon",
       subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine and Class",
       x = "City MPG",
       fill = "Drive Engine")+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")+
  theme_bw()
`stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cty, fill = factor(year),
             alpha = 0.5))+
  geom_histogram()+
  facet_wrap(~ drv,
             labeller = labeller(drv = c("4" = "four-wheel",
                                         "f" = "front-wheel",
                                         "r" = "rear-wheel")),
                                 ncol = 1)+
  theme_bw()+
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("cyan", "darkorchid"))+
  labs(title = "Histogram of City Miles per Gallon",
       subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine",
       x = "City Miles per Gallon",
       fill = "Year")
`stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cty, fill = drv))+
  geom_histogram()+
  facet_grid(rows = vars(drv),
             cols = vars(cyl))+
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("cyan", "darkorchid","firebrick1"),
                    label = c("Four-wheel",
                              "Front-wheel",
                              "Rear-Wheel"))+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")+
  labs(title = "Histogram of City Miels per Gallon")

1.5 5.任选两个定量变量，绘制散点图，在散点图上添加趋势线。

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy))+
  geom_point(col = "deepskyblue3")+
  geom_smooth(method = lm, se = F)+
  labs(title = "Scatter Diagram of Displacement and Highway MPG",
       x = "Displacement",
       y = "Highway MPG")+
  theme_bw()
`geom_smooth()` using formula = 'y ~ x'

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cty, hwy, col = I("deeppink3")))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method = lm, se = F, col = "deepskyblue")+
  labs(title = "Scatter Diagram of City MPG and Highway MPG",
       x = "City MPG",
       y = "Highway MPG")+
  theme_bw()
`geom_smooth()` using formula = 'y ~ x'

1.6 6.任选两个定量变量，绘制散点图，让散点的大小、颜色分别体现第3个、第4个变量的信息

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy, size = cyl, col = drv))+
  geom_point()+
  labs(title = "Scatter Diagram of Displacement and Highway MPG",
       subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine and Number of Cylinders",
       x = "Displacement",
       y = "Highway Miles per Gallon")+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("cyan", 
                                "darkorchid",
                                "deepskyblue3"))+
  theme_bw()

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cty, hwy, size = cyl, col = drv, alpha = 0.5))+
  geom_point()+
  labs(title = "Scatter Diagram of City MPG and Highway MPG",
       subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine and Number of Cylinders",
       x = "City MPG",
       y = "Highway MPG")+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("cyan", 
                                "darkorchid",
                                "deepskyblue3"))+
  theme_bw()

1.7 7.任选两个定量变量，一个定性变量，绘制分组散点图，添加趋势线

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy, col =drv))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method = lm, se = F)+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("cyan4", "darkorchid","deepskyblue"),
                    label = c("Four-wheel",
                              "Front-wheel",
                              "Rear-Wheel"))+
  labs(title = "Scatter Diagram of Displacement and Highway MPG",
       subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine",
       x = "Displacement",
       y = "Highway MPG")+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")+
  theme_bw()
`geom_smooth()` using formula = 'y ~ x'

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy, col = drv))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method = lm, se = F)+
  facet_wrap(~drv, ncol = 1,
             labeller = labeller(drv = c("4" = "four-wheel",
                                         "f" = "front-wheel",
                                         "r" = "rear-wheel")))+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("cyan4", "darkorchid","deepskyblue"))+
  labs(title = "Scatter Diagram of Displacement and Highway MPG",
       subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine",
       x = "Displacement",
       y = "Highway MPG")+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")+
  theme_bw()
`geom_smooth()` using formula = 'y ~ x'

1.8 8.任选两个定量变量，一个定性变量，绘制分组箱线图

mpg %>% 
  ggplot(aes(reorder(drv,cty), cty,col = drv))+
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(title = "Boxplot of City MPG",
       subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine",
       x = "Drive Engine",
       y = "City MPG")+
  theme_bw()

mpg %>% 
    ggplot(aes(reorder(drv, hwy), hwy,col = drv))+
    geom_boxplot() +
    coord_flip() +
    labs(title = "Boxplot of Highway MPG",
         subtitle = "Grouped by the Type of Drive Engine",
         x = "Drive Engine",
         y = "City MPG")+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")+
    theme_bw()

2 cellphone

library(readxl)
cellphone <- read_excel("cellphone.xlsx")
percent <- cellphone %>% 
  mutate(sex = recode(male, 
                      "0" = "female", 
                      "1" = "male"))%>% 
  group_by(sex,brand) %>% 
  tally() %>% 
  mutate(percent = n/sum(n))


percent %>% ggplot(aes(sex, percent, fill = brand))+
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "fill")+
  geom_text(aes(label = paste0(sprintf("%1.1f", percent*100),"%")),
            position = position_stack(vjust = 0.5), 
            colour = "white",
            size = 4)+
  theme_grey()+
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "PRGn")+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent)
